Stock Hawk App

This app is a project for the Udacity Android Developer nanodegree program. The first commits application code was provided by Udacity, and the projects premise was to productionize the code. Some user experience reviews were provided as a baseline guide on what aspects of the current app could use adjustment. I included the baseline specs of the app provided by Udacity, and Ill update with the production stats when the apps production ready.
